          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1657627629180-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the lamb is cooking, halve your <strong>cucumber</strong> lengthways then scrape out the seeds using a teaspoon, discard the seeds</p><p>Slice the <strong>cucumber halves</strong> finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Boil half a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-copy-2-1657627648624-x200.jpg",
